678
00:34:59,910 --> 00:35:00,600
Please forgive him.

679
00:35:00,600 --> 00:35:01,870
My buddy is a fierce man by nature.

680
00:35:01,870 --> 00:35:02,990
As long as the atmosphere is right,

681
00:35:02,990 --> 00:35:04,230
