707
00:35:46,790 --> 00:35:47,590
See you later.

708
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:49,240
This way, please.

709
00:35:58,710 --> 00:35:59,670
I'm Xia Zhu.

710
00:35:59,830 --> 00:36:01,430
