746
00:38:35,470 --> 00:38:37,760
I just want to play with my brother Chen Qi every day.

747
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:39,880
[Han Huaicheng, Duke Shengguo]

748
00:38:56,890 --> 00:38:57,490
Dear.

749
00:38:57,790 --> 00:39:00,170
